</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Night" /><category term="Long Exposure" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Traditional yakatabune rest on the Oigawa River beneath dramatic sunset clouds.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSCF1437.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSCF1437.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Ring in the Rain・雨の中のグランドリング</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251011/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Ring in the Rain・雨の中のグランドリング" /><published>2025-10-11T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-11T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/ring</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251011/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
