宝筐院の鮮やかな萱草。コダック エクター フィルムで撮影。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Temples" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A brilliant daylily at Hokyo-in temple, captured on Kodak Ektar film. 宝筐院の鮮やかな萱草。コダック エクター フィルムで撮影。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSC_1336-positive.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSC_1336-positive.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Togetsu Evening・渡月橋の夕方</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251007/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Togetsu Evening・渡月橋の夕方" /><published>2025-10-07T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-07T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/togetsu-night</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251007/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
