</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Night" /><category term="Long Exposure" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A long exposure in the last light of the evening, the Katsura River and Togetsu Bridge, with Mt. Ogura in the background. 桂川と渡月橋、小倉山を背景に夕暮れの最後の光で長時間露光。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSC_1303_x.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSC_1303_x.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Red Cherry Leaves・桜紅葉</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251006/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Red Cherry Leaves・桜紅葉" /><published>2025-10-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-10-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/red-cherry</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251006/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
