</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The leaves of the cherry trees turn color and fall, long before the maple leaves. Here are some in the morning sunlight at Arashiyama Park. 桜の葉はモミジよりもずっと早く色づき、そして散る。嵐山公園で朝日に照らされた葉である。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSC_1286.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2510_DSC_1286.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>